---
import { Rocket } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="relative py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="update-callout rounded-2xl p-6 border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 via-card/50 to-accent-2/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Rocket className="w-4 h-4 text-accent" aria-hidden="true" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="updates-heading mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
              Recent Updates
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-accent/20 text-accent border border-accent/30">
                v0.11.0
              </span>
            </h3>
            <button
              type="button"
              class="updates-toggle updates-toggle-compact"
              data-updates-toggle
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controls="older-updates"
              aria-label="Show full history"
              title="Show full history"
            >
              <span class="sr-only" data-updates-label>Show full history</span>
              <svg class="updates-chevron" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 rounded-xl border border-green-400/40 bg-green-500/15 px-4 py-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed">
              <Rocket className="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" aria-hidden="true" />
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-semibold bg-black text-green-300 border border-black leading-tight">JUST LAUNCHED</span>
              Obsidian Skill routing is now live with MCP + Obsidian context + Git CLI sync, including preflight checks and setup guidance.
              <a href="/skill" class="ml-1 inline font-semibold text-green-300 hover:text-green-200 underline decoration-green-300/70 underline-offset-2 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">See skill flows</a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.11.1 (April 2026):</span> Frontmatter updates now use AST-aware YAML preservation. Unmodified fields keep their original formatting: plain dates stay as <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code>, quoted strings keep their quotes, and <code>HH:MM</code> values are no longer misread as sexagesimal integers.
              (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/issues/77" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">#77</a>)
            </p>
          </div>

          <div id="older-updates" class="older-updates is-collapsed" data-updates-panel>
            <ul class="text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.11.0 (March 2026):</span> New <code>list_all_tags</code> tool scans the vault for all frontmatter tags and inline <code>#hashtags</code> with occurrence counts. Obsidian skill now routes to CLI for active file, daily notes, backlinks, and open-in-editor.
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/issues/80" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">#80</a>)
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.10.0 (March 2026):</span> New <code>createServer()</code> factory for library consumers. TypeScript declarations exported.
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/issues/84" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">#84</a>)
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.9.1 (March 2026):</span> Security fix: symlinks inside the vault that point outside the vault boundary are now blocked.
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/issues/78" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">#78</a>)
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.9.0 (March 2026):</span> Package renamed to <code>@bitbonsai/mcpvault</code> on npm at Obsidian's request. Update your config: replace <code>mcpvault</code> with <code>@bitbonsai/mcpvault</code>.
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.8.2 (March 2026):</span> Trailing-slash vault paths no longer truncate search results
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/48" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #48</a>),
                <code>get_vault_stats</code> now handles dotted folder names correctly
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/42" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #42</a>),
                note tools now support <code>.base</code> and <code>.canvas</code>
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/53" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #53</a>),
                string frontmatter inputs are now handled safely
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/47" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #47</a>),
                vault path is now optional for CLI usage (defaults to current working directory)
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/issues/50" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">#50</a>),
                and dependency refreshes for the MCP SDK and Node types are merged
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/43" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #43</a>,
                <a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/44" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #44</a>)
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.8.1:</span> Multi-word BM25 search relevance improvements
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/38" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #38</a>),
                patch_note undefined/null validation hardening
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/37" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">PR #37</a>),
                new <code>move_file</code> tool for binary-safe file moves with explicit path confirmation,
                binary filenames now visible in directory listings
                (<a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/issues/21" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">#21</a>)
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.7.5:</span> Search now matches note filenames,
                hidden directories filtered from listings, OpenCode install docs
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.7.4:</span> New get_vault_stats tool + improved error messages with remediation suggestions
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.7.3:</span> Bug fix for folder detection with dots in names + dependency updates
                <a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/15" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">(PR #15)</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-foreground">v0.7.2:</span> Security hardening - TOCTOU fixes, regex injection prevention, comprehensive CI/CD
                <a href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/pull/12" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-2 transition-colors">(PR #12)</a>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <a
              href="https://github.com/bitbonsai/mcpvault/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="updates-changelog-link"
            >
              <svg class="updates-changelog-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77 5.44 5.44 0 0 0 3.5 8.5c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path>
              </svg>
              See full changelog
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const initUpdatesToggle = () => {
    const updatesPanel = document.querySelector('[data-updates-panel]');
    const updatesToggle = document.querySelector('[data-updates-toggle]');
    const updatesLabel = document.querySelector('[data-updates-label]');

    if (!updatesPanel || !updatesToggle || !updatesLabel || updatesToggle.getAttribute('data-bound') === 'true') {
      return;
    }

    updatesToggle.setAttribute('data-bound', 'true');
    updatesToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const isExpanded = updatesToggle.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
      const nextExpanded = !isExpanded;
      const nextLabel = nextExpanded ? 'Show less' : 'Show full history';

      updatesToggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(nextExpanded));
      updatesToggle.setAttribute('aria-label', nextLabel);
      updatesToggle.setAttribute('title', nextLabel);
      updatesLabel.textContent = nextLabel;

      updatesPanel.classList.toggle('is-expanded', nextExpanded);
      updatesPanel.classList.toggle('is-collapsed', !nextExpanded);
      updatesToggle.classList.toggle('is-expanded', nextExpanded);
    });
  };

  initUpdatesToggle();
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', initUpdatesToggle);
</script>

<style>
  /* Update callout styling */
  .update-callout {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .update-callout::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1),
      transparent
    );
    transition: left 0.5s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .update-callout:hover::before {
    left: 100%;
  }

  .update-callout:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
  }

  .updates-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-right: 2.4rem;
  }

  .older-updates {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.35s ease;
  }

  .older-updates.is-collapsed {
    max-height: 2.5rem;
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, #000 0%, #000 58%, transparent 100%);
    mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, #000 0%, #000 58%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .older-updates.is-expanded {
    max-height: 48rem;
    -webkit-mask-image: none;
    mask-image: none;
  }

  .updates-changelog-link {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
    width: fit-content;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.42rem;
    color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.95);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .older-updates.is-expanded .updates-changelog-link {
    display: inline-flex;
  }

  .updates-changelog-link:hover {
    color: rgba(196, 181, 253, 1);
  }

  .updates-changelog-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.7);
    outline-offset: 2px;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
  }

  .updates-changelog-icon {
    width: 0.95rem;
    height: 0.95rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .updates-toggle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
    color: #ffffff;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .updates-toggle-compact {
    width: 1.65rem;
    height: 1.65rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: -0.35rem;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .updates-toggle:hover {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.25);
    border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.65);
  }

  .updates-toggle-compact:hover {
    transform: translateY(calc(-50% - 1px));
  }

  .updates-toggle:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.7);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .updates-chevron {
    width: 0.85rem;
    height: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .updates-toggle.is-expanded .updates-chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }
</style>
